aaos (0.1.2-1) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Fix Bug 13: agent-stop race with in-flight tool invocation.
    exec_task.abort() at all 4 streaming-handler sites now drains
    via tokio::time::timeout(&mut exec_task) for up to 500 ms before
    aborting, so pending file_write/git_commit calls complete
    before cancellation drops their futures.  race_deadline gains
    a tracing::warn so TTL-triggered drops are visible.
  * Fix Bug 17: inline_direct_plan no longer hardcodes the
    workspace param.  Direct-mode goals now write to the path
    the operator's goal text names instead of a workspace-internal
    output.md the operator can't easily find.
  * No new tests — both fixes verified end-to-end via droplet
    self-reflection runs.

